# Best AI Tools for Presentations & Content Creation
## 2024-2025 Guide

## AI Presentation Tools

### 1. Gamma.app ‚≠ê (Top Pick)
**What it does:** AI creates entire presentations from text prompts
**Best for:** Quick, beautiful decks without design skills
**Pricing:** Free tier, Pro $8/month

### 2. Beautiful.ai
**What it does:** Smart templates that auto-adjust
**Best for:** Data-heavy presentations
**Pricing:** Free trial, Pro $12/month

### 3. Tome
**What it does:** AI storytelling + presentations
**Best for:** Narrative-driven decks
**Pricing:** Free tier, Pro $8/month

### 4. Canva Magic Presentations
**What it does:** AI generates slides from prompts
**Best for:** Canva users who want speed
**Pricing:** Free with Canva Pro ($12.99/month)

